===Etymology===
:from the Latin ''exempli gratia'', meaning ''for example''

===[[adverb]]===
#for example
#:E.g. is used to sum up examples of a previous statement. The examples should never be exhaustive ([[i.e.]] should rather be used in that case) and should never be followed by [[et cetera]] or [[et cetera|etc.]] E.g. should be placed between parentheses when used in a written text and is always followed by a [[comma]] when used in it's function as 'for example'. 

===[[Example]]===
Asia is a large continent, with many large nations (e.g., China, India and Japan).